               <code code="34066-1" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="BOXED WARNING SECTION"/>
               <title>
                  <content styleCode="emphasis">WARNING</content>
               </title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>
                     <content styleCode="bold">ACCIDENTAL OVERDOSE OF IRON CONTAINING PRODUCTS IS A LEADING CAUSE OF FATAL POISONING IN CHILDREN UNDER 6. KEEP THIS PRODUCT OUT OF REACH OF CHILDREN. IN CASE OF ACCIDENTAL OVERDOSE, CALL A DOCTOR OR POISON CONTROL CENTER IMMEDIATELY.</content>
                  </paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20140506"/>
            </section>
